('siteminder', 'SiteMinder', 'Hotel channel manager and distribution platform connecting properties to 450+ booking channels',
 E'SiteMinder is the global hotel distribution platform used by over 44,000 properties to manage their presence across more than 450 booking channels - OTAs, GDS, direct booking engines, metasearch sites, and wholesale distributors. The core value proposition is rate and availability parity management: when a booking is made on Booking.com at 2am, SiteMinder''s two-way connection updates the room''s availability in real time across every other connected channel, preventing double-bookings and maintaining consistent inventory.\n\nThe channel manager supports two-way XML integrations with all major OTAs including Booking.com, Expedia, Airbnb, Agoda, and Ctrip, as well as GDS connections through Amadeus, Sabre, and Travelport. SiteMinder Little Hotelier is the company''s all-in-one PMS product designed for small hotels and bed and breakfasts that need a combined PMS and channel manager in one. SiteMinder''s standalone channel manager integrates with over 350 PMS and CRS platforms for properties that prefer to keep their existing property management system.\n\nSiteMinder Insights provides demand forecasting and rate intelligence based on market data, helping revenue managers identify optimal pricing windows for their destination and property type. The platform also includes a direct booking engine that can be installed on the hotel''s website to capture direct reservations at lower commission cost than OTA bookings.\n\nSiteMinder is the most widely deployed hotel channel manager globally and is particularly strong in the Asia Pacific, Europe, and Middle East markets. The platform processes over 100 million reservations annually, providing the scale of connectivity data that underlies its market intelligence tools.',
 'https://siteminder.com', 'https://siteminder.com',
