 ARRAY['Connects to 450+ booking channels with real-time two-way rate and availability sync', 'Two-way integrations with 350+ PMS and CRS platforms for flexible deployment', 'SiteMinder Insights provides demand forecasting and competitor rate intelligence', 'Most widely deployed hotel channel manager globally with proven scale at 44,000+ properties'],
