('atomize', 'Atomize', 'AI revenue management system for hotels with fully automated dynamic pricing',
 E'Atomize is an AI-native revenue management system built for independent hotels and small chains that want fully automated dynamic pricing without the implementation complexity and cost of enterprise RMS platforms. The platform''s core differentiator is automation depth - rather than generating pricing recommendations that a revenue manager must review and approve, Atomize can operate in fully automated mode, pushing rate updates to the hotel''s PMS and channel manager continuously without human intervention.\n\nThe pricing engine analyses demand signals in real time: pickup pace by room type and date, competitor rate movements, local event calendars, weather patterns, and historical booking curves to calculate the optimal rate for each room type and booking window. In automated mode, rates update multiple times per day across all connected distribution channels, capturing demand spikes and adjusting for soft periods without requiring a dedicated revenue manager on call.\n\nFor independent hotels that cannot afford a full-time revenue manager or an enterprise RMS like IDeaS or Duetto, Atomize provides professional-grade dynamic pricing at a price point accessible to properties with 20-200 rooms. The setup process is designed for properties without dedicated IT support - the integration with most major PMS platforms is configured within a few days, and the AI begins generating recommendations from historical booking data within the first week.\n\nAtomize is particularly well-deployed across the Nordic hotel market where the company was founded, and has expanded significantly across Europe and into North America. Properties using Atomize typically report 10-15% revenue per available room improvements in the first year compared to manual rate-setting practices.',
 'https://atomize.com', 'https://atomize.com',
