 ARRAY['Fully automated mode pushes rate updates continuously without revenue manager approval required', 'Accessible price point for independent hotels that cannot justify enterprise RMS licensing', 'Fast setup - PMS integration typically configured within a few days without IT support', 'Real-time demand signal analysis captures pricing opportunities that weekly manual reviews miss'],
 ARRAY['Fully automated pricing requires trusting the AI - some revenue managers prefer review-and-approve workflows', 'Less customisation depth than enterprise RMS platforms for complex mixed-use or casino properties', 'Reporting and analytics are functional but less comprehensive than Duetto or IDeaS', 'Best suited to standard hotel operations - complex group or wholesale rate management is less mature'],
