('hopper', 'Hopper', 'AI-powered travel booking app with price prediction and flexible trip protection',
 E'Hopper is a consumer travel booking app that uses AI price prediction to help travelers know when to book flights and hotels at the best price, and offers a suite of flexible travel products that protect against the financial risk of trip changes. The company has grown from a price-watching app into one of the largest consumer travel platforms in North America, processing billions of dollars in travel bookings annually.\n\nThe core AI feature is price prediction: Hopper''s models analyse hundreds of billions of historical flight and hotel prices to forecast whether current prices will rise or fall, and give travelers a recommendation to book now or wait with a percentage confidence rating. Travelers who trust the recommendation to wait and see prices rise receive a refund of the difference through Hopper''s Price Freeze product. This turns price uncertainty from a source of anxiety into a managed risk.\n\nHopper''s financial products layer on top of the booking experience and generate a significant portion of the company''s revenue: Cancel for Any Reason allows travelers to cancel a non-refundable booking for any reason and receive a travel credit, Change for Any Reason allows free flight changes, and Price Drop Guarantee refunds the difference if prices drop after booking. These products are priced as add-ons and give travelers the flexibility of fully refundable tickets without paying airline refundable fares.\n\nHopper is a free app for consumers with no subscription cost. Revenue comes from travel supplier commissions and the financial protection product add-ons. The platform is available in the US, Canada, and UK and covers flights, hotels, rental cars, and vacation packages. For budget-conscious travelers who want AI-powered price guidance and flexible trip protection without booking directly with airlines, Hopper provides genuine value not available through traditional OTAs.',
 'https://hopper.com', 'https://hopper.com',
 'free', true, 0, 4.3, 5600, false, false, false,
 ARRAY['travel', 'business-travel', 'productivity'],
 ARRAY['AI price prediction tells travelers when to book for lowest fares with confidence percentages', 'Price Freeze locks in current price while traveler decides without commitment risk', 'Cancel and Change for Any Reason products add flexibility to non-refundable bookings', 'Free app for consumers - no subscription or membership required to access predictions'],
 ARRAY['Price predictions are probabilistic - accuracy varies by route and booking window length', 'Financial protection add-on products increase total trip cost if used on every booking', 'Primarily consumer-focused - corporate travel policy management is limited vs Navan or TripActions', 'Inventory and supplier relationships are strong in North America but thinner internationally'],
 ARRAY['Budget-conscious travelers optimising flight booking timing with AI price guidance', 'Travelers who want cancel or change flexibility without paying airline refundable fare premiums', 'Consumers comparing hotel and flight prices with real-time AI-based booking recommendations'],
